dfischer.utils

Class PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapKey

  • public class PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapKey
extends java.lang.Object
    Key-object for the PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMap. Contains a status type and a HTTP status code for similar failed URL calls.
    See Also:
    PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMap, HttpTestURL.getStatusType(), HttpTestURL.getStatus()
